---
// Hero.astro - Teaser section with project overview

const basePath = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
---
<section id="hero" class="content-section hero-section">
  <div class="title-wrapper">
    <div class="title-with-logo">
      <img src={`${basePath}icon.png`} alt="RV-Filter Logo" class="title-logo">
      <h1 class="main-title" id="animated-title">RAGEN-V2</h1>
    </div>
    <p class="title-subtitle">Understanding Reasoning Collapse in Multi-Turn Agent&nbsp;Reinforcement&nbsp;Learning</p>
  </div>

  <p class="main-subtitle">
    Even when entropy stays high, agents can quietly stop listening to inputs — producing fluent but input-agnostic boilerplate. We call this <strong>template collapse</strong>.
  </p>

  <div class="authors-section compact">
    <div class="authors-list">
      <p class="author-line">
        <a href="https://zihanwang314.github.io/">Zenus Wang</a><sup>*&dagger;1</sup>,
        <a href="https://chigui0.github.io/">Chi Gui</a><sup>&dagger;2</sup>,
        <a href="#">Xing Jin</a><sup>&dagger;3</sup>,
        <a href="https://qinengwang-aiden.github.io/">Qineng Wang</a><sup>&dagger;1</sup>,
        <a href="https://lichengliu03.github.io/">Licheng Liu</a><sup>&dagger;4</sup>,
        <a href="https://jameskrw.github.io/">Kangrui Wang</a><sup>1</sup>
      </p>
      <p class="author-line">
        <a href="https://shiqichen17.github.io/">Shiqi Chen</a><sup>5</sup>,
        <a href="https://scholar.google.com/citations?user=WR875gYAAAAJ&hl=en">Linjie Li</a><sup>6</sup>,
        <a href="https://zyang-ur.github.io/">Zhengyuan Yang</a><sup>7</sup>,
        <a href="https://williamzhangsjtu.github.io/">Pingyue Zhang</a><sup>1</sup>,
        <a href="https://2prime.github.io/">Yiping Lu</a><sup>1</sup>,
        <a href="https://jiajunwu.com/">Jiajun Wu</a><sup>8</sup>,
        <a href="https://profiles.stanford.edu/fei-fei-li">Li Fei-Fei</a><sup>8</sup>
      </p>
      <p class="author-line">
        <a href="https://www.microsoft.com/en-us/research/people/lijuanw/">Lijuan Wang</a><sup>7</sup>,
        <a href="https://homes.cs.washington.edu/~yejin/">Yejin Choi</a><sup>8</sup>,
        <a href="https://limanling.github.io/">Manling Li</a><sup>1</sup>
      </p>
      <p class="equal-contribution">
        <sup>&dagger;</sup> Core Contributors &nbsp;&nbsp; <sup>*</sup> Project Lead
      </p>
      <p class="affiliations">
        <sup>1</sup>Northwestern University &nbsp;
        <sup>2</sup>UIUC &nbsp;
        <sup>3</sup>University of British Columbia &nbsp;
        <sup>4</sup>Imperial College London &nbsp;
        <sup>5</sup>City University of Hong Kong &nbsp;
        <sup>6</sup>University of Washington &nbsp;
        <sup>7</sup>Microsoft &nbsp;
        <sup>8</sup>Stanford University
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="resources-section">
    <div class="resources-buttons">
      <a href="https://github.com/RAGEN-AI/RAGEN" class="cta-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 16 16" class="button-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M8 0C3.58 0 0 3.58 0 8c0 3.54 2.29 6.53 5.47 7.59.4.07.55-.17.55-.38 0-.19-.01-.82-.01-1.49-2.01.37-2.53-.49-2.69-.94-.09-.23-.48-.94-.82-1.13-.28-.15-.68-.52-.01-.53.63-.01 1.08.58 1.23.82.72 1.21 1.87.87 2.33.66.07-.52.28-.87.51-1.07-1.78-.2-3.64-.89-3.64-3.95 0-.87.31-1.59.82-2.15-.08-.2-.36-1.02.08-2.12 0 0 .67-.21 2.2.82.64-.18 1.32-.27 2-.27s1.36.09 2 .27c1.53-1.04 2.2-.82 2.2-.82.44 1.1.16 1.92.08 2.12.51.56.82 1.27.82 2.15 0 3.07-1.87 3.75-3.65 3.95.29.25.54.73.54 1.48 0 1.07-.01 1.93-.01 2.2 0 .21.15.46.55.38A8.013 8.013 0 0 0 16 8c0-4.42-3.58-8-8-8z"></path>
        </svg>
        <span class="button-text">Code</span>
        <div class="repo-stats">
          <div class="stat-item">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="currentColor">
              <path d="M8 .25a.75.75 0 0 1 .673.418l1.882 3.815 4.21.612a.75.75 0 0 1 .416 1.279l-3.046 2.97.719 4.192a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088.791L8 12.347l-3.766 1.98a.75.75 0 0 1-1.088-.79l.72-4.194L.818 6.374a.75.75 0 0 1 .416-1.28l4.21-.611L7.327.668A.75.75 0 0 1 8 .25z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span id="hero-stars-count">1.4k</span>
          </div>
          <div class="stat-item">
            <svg aria-hidden="true" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" width="16" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M5 3.25a.75.75 0 11-1.5 0 .75.75 0 011.5 0zm0 2.122a2.25 2.25 0 10-1.5 0v.878A2.25 2.25 0 005.75 8.5h1.5v2.128a2.251 2.251 0 101.5 0V8.5h1.5a2.25 2.25 0 002.25-2.25v-.878a2.25 2.25 0 10-1.5 0v.878a.75.75 0 01-.75.75h-4.5A.75.75 0 015 6.25v-.878zm3.75 7.378a.75.75 0 11-1.5 0 .75.75 0 011.5 0zm3-8.75a.75.75 0 100-1.5.75.75 0 000 1.5z"></path>
            </svg>
            <span id="hero-forks-count">105</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </a>
      <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/2504.20073" class="resource-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="resource-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M14 2H6a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v16a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h12a2 2 0 0 0 2-2V8l-6-6z"></path>
          <polyline points="14 2 14 8 20 8"></polyline>
          <line x1="16" y1="13" x2="8" y2="13"></line>
          <line x1="16" y1="17" x2="8" y2="17"></line>
          <polyline points="10 9 9 9 8 9"></polyline>
        </svg>
        <span>Paper</span>
      </a>
      <a href="https://x.com/wzihanw/status/1915052871474712858" class="resource-button" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" class="resource-icon x-icon" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M18.244 2.25h3.308l-7.227 8.26 8.502 11.24H16.17l-5.214-6.817L4.99 21.75H1.68l7.73-8.835L1.254 2.25H8.08l4.713 6.231zm-1.161 17.52h1.833L7.084 4.126H5.117z"></path>
        </svg>
        <span>tl;dr</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#citation" class="resource-button">
        <i class="fas fa-file-alt resource-icon"></i>
        <span>Citation</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/v1/" class="resource-button">
        <i class="fas fa-arrow-left resource-icon"></i>
        <span>RAGEN V1</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

</section>

<script>
  // Format numbers to show 'k' for thousands
  function formatNumber(num) {
    return num > 999 ? (num / 1000).toFixed(1) + 'k' : num;
  }

  // Fetch GitHub stats directly
  async function fetchGitHubStats() {
    try {
      const starsElement = document.getElementById('hero-stars-count');
      const forksElement = document.getElementById('hero-forks-count');

      const response = await fetch('https://api.github.com/repos/RAGEN-AI/RAGEN');
      const data = await response.json();

      const stars = data.stargazers_count;
      const forks = data.forks_count;

      if (starsElement && stars !== undefined) {
        const formattedStars = formatNumber(stars);
        if (formattedStars !== '1.4k') {
          starsElement.textContent = formattedStars;
        }
      }

      if (forksElement && forks !== undefined) {
        const formattedForks = formatNumber(forks);
        if (formattedForks !== '105') {
          forksElement.textContent = formattedForks;
        }
      }
    } catch (error) {
      console.error('Error fetching GitHub stats:', error);
    }
  }

  document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', () => {
    fetchGitHubStats();

    const titleElement = document.getElementById('animated-title');
    const subtitleElement = document.querySelector('.title-subtitle');

    if (titleElement) {
      const text = titleElement.textContent || '';
      titleElement.innerHTML = '';
      text.split('').forEach((char, index) => {
        const span = document.createElement('span');
        span.textContent = char === ' ' ? '\u00A0' : char;
        span.className = 'reveal-char';
        span.style.animationDelay = `${index * 0.05}s`;
        titleElement.appendChild(span);
      });
    }

    if (subtitleElement) {
      const text = subtitleElement.textContent || '';
      subtitleElement.innerHTML = '';
      // Split into words, group "Agent Reinforcement Learning" as non-breaking
      const noBreakPhrases = ['Agent Reinforcement Learning'];
      const words = text.trim().split(/\s+/);
      let charIndex = 0;
      let wordIdx = 0;
      while (wordIdx < words.length) {
        // Check if current position starts a no-break phrase
        let matched = null;
        for (const phrase of noBreakPhrases) {
          const phraseWords = phrase.split(/\s+/);
          if (words.slice(wordIdx, wordIdx + phraseWords.length).join(' ') === phrase) {
            matched = phraseWords;
            break;
          }
        }

        if (wordIdx > 0) {
          // Add a regular space (allows line break before this word/group)
          const spaceSpan = document.createElement('span');
          spaceSpan.textContent = '\u00A0';
          spaceSpan.className = 'reveal-char-subtitle';
          spaceSpan.style.animationDelay = `${0.8 + charIndex * 0.02}s`;
          subtitleElement.appendChild(spaceSpan);
          charIndex++;
        }

        if (matched) {
          // Wrap the entire phrase in a nowrap container
          const wrapper = document.createElement('span');
          wrapper.style.whiteSpace = 'nowrap';
          const phraseText = matched.join(' ');
          for (let i = 0; i < phraseText.length; i++) {
            const ch = phraseText[i];
            const span = document.createElement('span');
            span.textContent = ch === ' ' ? '\u00A0' : ch;
            span.className = 'reveal-char-subtitle';
            span.style.animationDelay = `${0.8 + charIndex * 0.02}s`;
            wrapper.appendChild(span);
            charIndex++;
          }
          subtitleElement.appendChild(wrapper);
          wordIdx += matched.length;
        } else {
          // Regular word
          const word = words[wordIdx];
          for (const ch of word) {
            const span = document.createElement('span');
            span.textContent = ch;
            span.className = 'reveal-char-subtitle';
            span.style.animationDelay = `${0.8 + charIndex * 0.02}s`;
            subtitleElement.appendChild(span);
            charIndex++;
          }
          wordIdx++;
        }
      }
    }
  });
</script>

<style>
  .main-subtitle {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 16px auto 0.8rem;
    color: #444;
    font-size: 19px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    text-align: center;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .authors-section.compact {
    margin-top: 1.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .anonymous-authors {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: #333;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .venue-line {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: #777;
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .cta-button {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 11px 22px;
    background: linear-gradient(45deg, #2a2f6c, #4b4f8f);
    border: none;
    border-radius: 50px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(42, 47, 108, 0.2);
  }

  .cta-button:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 6px 20px rgba(42, 47, 108, 0.3);
    text-decoration: none;
    color: white;
  }

  .button-icon {
    width: 20px;
    height: 20px;
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .button-text {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: white;
    margin-right: 12px;
  }

  .repo-stats {
    display: flex;
    gap: 16px;
    padding-left: 16px;
    border-left: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
  }

  .stat-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .stat-item svg {
    fill: currentColor;
  }

  .equal-contribution {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #666;
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .resources-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .figure-caption {
    max-width: 820px;
    margin: 1rem auto 0;
    font-size: 0.92rem;
    color: #666;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-align: center;
  }
</style>
